00:38:09.780 --> 00:38:11.300 align:middle line:90%
Well, they had happy.

00:38:11.300 --> 00:38:11.735 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: And that's something.

00:38:11.735 --> 00:38:12.530 align:middle line:90%
>>SOWAH: [LAUGHS]

00:38:12.530 --> 00:38:14.630 align:middle line:84%
>>SUE: That's something everyone
