00:38:14.630 --> 00:38:15.570 align:middle line:90%
is the happy.

00:38:15.570 --> 00:38:19.700 align:middle line:84%
>>SOWAH: So how I have conceived
of this whole picture is

00:38:19.700 --> 00:38:23.485 align:middle line:84%
