is an emotional being,

00:38:23.485 --> 00:38:25.850 align:middle line:84%
is a physical being,
is a spiritual being,

00:38:25.850 --> 00:38:28.030 align:middle line:84%
is a social being,
is a psychological

00:38:28.030 --> 00:38:31.850 align:middle line:84%
being, yeah, then
what that means

00:38:31.850 --> 00:38:35.870 align:middle line:84%
is that for a person to
be well, that person needs

00:38:35.870 --> 00:38:39.540 align:middle line:90%
to grow in all these areas.

00:38:39.540 --> 00:38:40.760 align:middle line:90%
So if I see kids--

00:38:40.760 --> 00:38:42.530 align:middle line:90%
I mean, growing up myself--

00:38:42.530 --> 00:38:50.990 align:middle line:84%
that sense of freedom to
go out and fend for myself,

00:38:50.990 --> 00:38:53.670 align:middle line:84%
the freedom to create, make
my own toys-- that freedom

00:38:53.670 --> 00:38:58.250 align:middle line:84%
to be in fights and
still come out strong,

00:38:58.250 --> 00:39:04.600 align:middle line:84%
or that feeling a sense of
belonging in a community, yeah?

00:39:04.600 --> 00:39:05.400 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: Yeah.

00:39:05.400 --> 00:39:06.840 align:middle line:90%
>>SOWAH: All those where--

00:39:06.840 --> 00:39:13.020 align:middle line:84%
I call them emotional weights to
build your emotional strength--

00:39:13.020 --> 00:39:16.770 align:middle line:84%
the spiritual
weights, the social.

00:39:16.770 --> 00:39:21.300 align:middle line:84%
All those challenges are
weights for your growth.

00:39:21.300 --> 00:39:24.060 align:middle line:84%
Just that some people
would go and lift

00:39:24.060 --> 00:39:28.890 align:middle line:84%
weights physically to
build, what I see is this.

00:39:28.890 --> 00:39:31.710 align:middle line:84%
If you have all
your material needs

00:39:31.710 --> 00:39:37.420 align:middle line:84%
met and you have all your
physical needs met, yeah,

00:39:37.420 --> 00:39:40.540 align:middle line:84%
and for some reason,
emotionally you struggle--

00:39:40.540 --> 00:39:46.060 align:middle line:84%
spiritually bankrupt,
socially unskilled,

00:39:46.060 --> 00:39:49.160 align:middle line:90%
psychologically unbalanced--

00:39:49.160 --> 00:39:53.870 align:middle line:84%
now, you don't want to
tell me you're rich.

00:39:53.870 --> 00:39:58.940 align:middle line:84%
You don't want to tell me you
have all the things you want.

00:39:58.940 --> 00:40:01.700 align:middle line:84%
If you tell me that, it means
you're seeing yourself only

00:40:01.700 --> 00:40:04.170 align:middle line:90%
as a physical being.

00:40:04.170 --> 00:40:08.520 align:middle line:84%
But if you are a physical,
emotional, spiritual, social,

00:40:08.520 --> 00:40:13.460 align:middle line:84%
and psychological mental
being, then maybe you

00:40:13.460 --> 00:40:16.440 align:middle line:84%
might want to consider
these as necessary

00:40:16.440 --> 00:40:19.590 align:middle line:84%
so that you have actually
got all you need.

00:40:19.590 --> 00:40:26.630 align:middle line:84%
Now, if you find
somebody who, physically,

00:40:26.630 --> 00:40:32.060 align:middle line:90%
emotionally, they are resilient.

00:40:32.060 --> 00:40:35.630 align:middle line:84%
They can laugh in the
face of challenge.

00:40:35.630 --> 00:40:38.120 align:middle line:90%
They can overcome trauma.

00:40:38.120 --> 00:40:38.920 align:middle line:90%
Yeah?

00:40:38.920 --> 00:40:39.720 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: Yeah.

00:40:39.720 --> 00:40:41.930 align:middle line:84%
>>SOWAH: But they
don't have shoes,

00:40:41.930 --> 00:40:44.360 align:middle line:90%
maybe we can ship shoes to them.

00:40:44.360 --> 00:40:47.660 align:middle line:90%
We can ship food.

00:40:47.660 --> 00:40:52.830 align:middle line:84%
But if a person is emotionally,
spiritually bankrupt,

00:40:52.830 --> 00:40:55.390 align:middle line:90%
there is not much we can ship.

00:40:55.390 --> 00:40:59.680 align:middle line:84%
These are things that
are life-long processes

00:40:59.680 --> 00:41:01.840 align:middle line:90%
of cultivating.

00:41:01.840 --> 00:41:04.810 align:middle line:10%
And if you don't have
it, you can't go buy it.

00:41:04.810 --> 00:41:05.610 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:41:05.610 --> 00:41:08.130 align:middle line:90%
I think these are crucial.

00:41:08.130 --> 00:41:11.340 align:middle line:84%
The spiritual, emotional,
social, and stuff

00:41:11.340 --> 00:41:15.145 align:middle line:84%
are overlooked in our
evaluation of what good life is.

00:41:15.145 --> 00:41:16.270 align:middle line:90%
>>SUE: Couldn't agree more.

00:41:16.270 --> 00:41:17.260 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely.

00:41:17.260 --> 00:41:20.090 align:middle line:84%
We have to approach it from
this whole person perspective.

00:41:20.090 --> 00:41:20.890 align:middle line:90%
>>SOWAH: Mm-hmm.

00:41:20.890 --> 00:41:23.410 align:middle line:84%
>>SUE: Can you give us
