00:42:05.660 --> 00:42:11.980 align:middle line:10%
I've seen students overcome
their fears, gotten

00:42:11.980 --> 00:42:16.090 align:middle line:10%
their depression under control,
eating disorder under control,

00:42:16.090 --> 00:42:19.180 align:middle line:10%
social anxiety under control--

00:42:19.180 --> 00:42:22.480 align:middle line:10%
not because we do
anything specifically

00:42:22.480 --> 00:42:24.580 align:middle line:10%
to address any of these things.

00:42:24.580 --> 00:42:29.380 align:middle line:84%
But what I believe is, if a
person lives in a community

00:42:29.380 --> 00:42:34.030 align:middle line:84%
